data.description: Buyer Bonus! $10,000 Seller credit towards buyers closing costs or interest rate buy down! Welcome to Sterling Meadows one of the best neighborhoods in Elk Grove! Built in 2021, this 5 bedroom 3 Full bath home has everything you need. Perfect for an investment property or growing family  featuring 2,140 sqft of living space this home has all the classy upgrades that will make you sing. Granite counters surround the chef inspired kitchen perfect for entertaining with double built-in ovens and gas range. The home also features a downstairs bedroom perfect for guest or family, that is right next to a full bathroom. Close to 99, Kaiser, Sky River Casino, shopping and Flatland Brewery, the location is perfect! Only a block away from the new Entrican park. Enjoy low utility bills with the leased solar system! Come tour this home this weekend! 3D-Tour available. Welcome Home
